Speedbreaker realized that he was in trouble, and quickly rolled over
twice, back on to his stomach, and transformed. Before he could get
running however the explosive shells exploded, and sent his car mode
hurteling a few feet away, as he hit a rock hard. He groaned hard, and
stopped.

Wildrider was getting close to Incarcinerator. The smoke that encirlced
a crater was finally clearing. He saw a little cassette on fire. He
transformed, and quickly picked it up and shook of the flamed. He then
inserted it into his car radio system. He then took to the air, heading
towards Incarcinerator, and opened fire with his laser gun. Pulling the
trigger only once (eight shots though).

Cliffjumpr decided to change his tactics, and got under First Aid to
help him to his feet.

Firedrill put up another arm to block another sword slice from
Headstrong, then sent a fist straight into the Rino's face. Headstrong
backed away a bit. Firedrill tried his best to remain between Headstrong
and the dammaged Protectobots.
